PrecisAmendments to the EXPORT CONTROL LIST which update the lists of all strategic and military goods for which an export permit is required. Amendments include the Industrial List, the Munition List and the Atomic Energy List of the Coordinating Committee for Multilateral Strategic Export Controls (COCOM), as well as other multilateral lists.
